title: "WD Purple WD10PURX - Surveillance hard drive 1TB" " WD 1TB Internal Desktop Hard Drives CDWG.com
description: "WD Purple Surveillance Storage offers exclusive AllFrame technology to bring you premium reliability and peace-of-mind when installing your home or small to medium business security system. WD Purple's exclusive firmware upgrades work with ATA streaming to reduce error pixilation and video interruptions that occur when desktop hard drives are incorrectly used as storage in security systems. WD Purple Surveillance Storage is built for 24/7, always-on, high-definition surveillance security systems that use up to eight hard drives and up to 32 cameras.You wouldn't use a bicycle to transport cargo across the country because it's not the right tool for the job. You also shouldn't use a desktop hard drive in your surveillance security system because it wasn't designed for that application. WD Purple surveillance-class storage has been tested to be compatible in a wide-range of security systems. These drives are designed to replace standard desktop drives that were not designed for the harsh 24/7 always-on, high-definition surveillance environment. Desktop drives are built to run for only short intervals and are not engineered to withstand high-temperature fluctuations and equipment vibrations found in a typical surveillance application."

title: "GA-H170N-WIFI LGA1150 Motherboard "@en Motherboard"@en
description:
"The GA-H170N-WIFI offers a wealth of connections and features including USB 3.0 and a choice of three monitor connection standards - DVI and two HDMI ports, all of which can be used simultaneously if required.
GIGABYTE 100 series motherboards support the latest 6th Generation Intel Core processors, a 14nm desktop CPU which features improved performance, power efficiency and support for DDR4 memory, bringing cutting edge features and ultimate performance to your next PC build.
FeaturesSocket 1151 Mini ITX motherboard with Intel H170 Express chipsetIntegrated Wi-Fi and Bluetooth2x DDR4 DIMM sockets (max. 32 GB)2x HDMI + DVI (up to 3 ports simultaneously)32Gb/s PCIe Gen3 M.2 port4x USB3.0 and 1x USB3.1 Type-C2x LAN ports, HD Audio and optical S/PDIF Out
Connecting the Future - USB Type-C
The USB Type-C port with USB 3.0 support is a robust and slim connector for all of your devices with reversible plug orientation.
Fast Onboard Storage with 32Gb/s M.2
GIGABYTE M.2 solution offers considerably faster storage performance and support for both PCIe and SATA interface for M.2 SSD devices.
Dual Intel GbE LAN with cFosSpeed
The Dual Intel Gigabit LAN with cFosSpeed features advanced technology to help deliver better network responsiveness in crowded LAN environments and allows optimisation and improved network performance for specific applications, making it a popular choice amongst gamers.
Faster and Better Coverage with Intel Dual Band 802.11ac Wi-Fi + BT4.2 Module
The on-board 802.11ac Wi-Fi module from Intel supports up to 867 Mb/s wireless networks and Bluetooth 4.2. The bonded 2.4GHz/5GHz Dual Band and 2T2R antenna expands your coverage.
High Definition Audio Design
The Realtek ALC1150 is a high-performance multi-channel high definition audio codec that delivers an exceptional audio listening experience with up to 115dB SNR, ensuring users get the best possible audio quality from their PC. High Quality audio capacitors with LED Trace Path Lighting deliver the highest quality sound resolution and sound expansion to create the most realistic sound effects for professional gamers.
4K Ultra HD Support
4K resolution is the next technological milestone in high-definition content delivery, utilising approximately 4,000 pixels on the horizontal axis, more than four times today's standard HD pixel density. GIGABYTE motherboards provide native 4K support with integrated Intel HD Graphics via HDMI.
Rear ports"@en

title: "Corsair Air Series AF120 LED Quiet Edition High Airflow Fan Single Pack - White"@en-US "Computer Accessories & Peripherals Page 121 | Laptops Outlet Direct"@en-US
description: "Superior cooling performance and LED illumination Corsair Air Series LED high airflow PC case fans combine efficient, low-noise airflow with striking LED lighting. The custom-molded blades are designed for high-volume air delivery with less noise and turbulence than typical case fans. They're translucent, with a frosted texture, so the light from the four LEDs adds a dramatic effect.Tuned for high-airflow, large volume cooling Air Series AF fan models perform best in unrestricted spaces with at least 3cm of clearance, and they're ideal for mounting at the rear or top of your PC case as exhaust fans for your PC's motherboard and CPU, graphics accelerators, and other components that fill the case with heat. They work equally well as unrestricted intake fans for areas like side panels or bottom intakes. For high restriction areas like hard drive cages or in other tight spaces where there's less air volume, check out our Air Series SP models of high static pressure fans."@en-US

title: "Placa Rede TP-Link Wireless N 150Mbps PCI-e"@pt PCI-e (TL-WN781ND) - PCDIGA"@pt
description: "O que este produto fazO TP-LINK TL-WN781ND é projetado para fornecer completo desempenho Wireless de ponta a ponta do servidor ou backbone para a infraestrtutura do switch e ambiente de trabalho através do conector PCI Express. O adaptador TL-WN781ND Wireless N PCI Express (x1) fornece uma maior compatibilidade de instalação adaptando-se com qualquer padrão PCI slot Express x1 x2 x8 ou x16. Em comparação com placas de rede padrão PCI ele oferece maior largura de banda confiabilidade e maior funcionalidade permitindo-lhe desfrutar de uma conexão rápida e avançada fazendo download chamadas via internet e assistindo vídeos em HD.Velocidade & Alcance Wireless NConforme o padrão IEEE 802.11n o TL-WN781ND pode facilmente estabelecer uma rede sem fios e chegar a uma velocidade de até 9X e a um alcance de até 4x dos alcançados por produtos convencionais 11g. Comparado com os produtos de origem 54M o TL-WN781ND oferece melhorias de desempenho permitindo que você tenha uma experiência mais satisfatória enquanto navega compartilha arquivos ou assiste vídeos em alta resolução.Criptografias WPA / WPA2 - Segurança AvançadaAssim como para a segurança da conexão WI-FI a criptografia WEP não tem sido a mais segura e eficiente para detecção de invasões externas. O TL-WN781ND fornece criptografia WPA/WPA2 que são criados pelo grupo industrial WI-FI Alliance protegendo a rede Wireless contra ameaças externas.Rápida Configuração de SegurançaCompatível com WI-FI Protected Setup ™ (WPS) o recurso de Configuração de Segurança Rápida (QSS) do TL-WN781ND é ideal para criar uma conexão criptografada WPA evitando a invasão externa e além disso maximizar os recursos de gerenciamento. Não somente mais rápida do que as configurações de segurança normais mas de forma mais prática em que você não precisa de se lembrar de uma senha!Antena DestacávelO TL-WN781ND possui uma antena externa que pode ser rotacionada e direcionada em diferentes direções para se ajustar a vários ambientes de operação e pode trazer um melhor desempenho do que a antena interna. Mesmo para aplicações mais exigentes a antena pode ser substituída por diferentes modelos de antenas apresentando maior flexibilidade e maior cobertura wireless.Interface: PCI ExpressDimensões: 120.8 x 78.5 x 21.5mm (W X D X H)Tipo de Antena: Onidirecional DestacávelGanho de Antena: 2dBiNormas Wireless: IEEE 802.11n IEEE 802.11g IEEE 802.11bFrequência Wireless: 2.400-2.4835GHzTaxa de Sinal:11n: Up to 150Mbps(dinâmico)11g: Up to 54Mbps(dinâmico)11b: Up to 11Mbps(dinâmico)EIRP: <20dBm(EIRP)Sensibilidade de Recepção:130M: -68dBm@10% PER108M: -68dBm@10% PER54M: -68dBm@10% PER11M: -85dBm@8% PER6M: -88dBm@10% PER1M: -90dBm@8% PERModos Wireless: Ad-Hoc / modo InfraestruturaSegurança Wireless: Suporta WEP de 64/128 bits WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK Filtragem MAC WirelessTecnologia de Modulação: DBPSK DQPSK CCK OFDM 16-QAM 64-QAMCertificações: CE FCC RoHSConteúdo da Embalagem:Adaptador WirelessAntena Onidirecional DestacávelCD de RecursosGuia de Instalação Rápida"@pt

title: "Placa Som Asus Xonar Essence STX II 7.1"@pt 7.1 (90YA00NN-M0UA00) - PCDIGA"@pt
description: "Placa de som com 7.1 canais e qualidade Hi-Fi com 124dB SNR e amplificador de topo para auscultadores.Qualidade de áudio 124dB SNR (signal-to-noise ratio) de topo herdada da revolucionária e amplamente elogiada - Xonar Essence ST/STXLatência ultrareduzida com o fonte de relógio TCXO premiumFonte de alimentação estável e consistente graças aos reguladores LDO (low-dropout) de alta fidelidade e condensadores WIMA® para um som inigualávelAmplificador de topo para auscultadores suportam uma impedância até 600ohm com ganhos adicionais para monitores de ouvido (IEMs - in-ear monitors)O kit de troca op-amp exclusivo inclui três op-amps e ferramentas para fácil afinação dos tonsOs op-amps MUSES conhecidos proporcionam uma musicalidade realistaUltra-fidelidade (120dB SNR) com saída para 7.1 canais através da daughterboard exclusivaMantendo o espírito e filosofia audiófila vivaQuatro anos depois da estreia da Essence STX - durante muito tempo detentora da 1ª posição do segmento das Placas de Som Head-Fi\s através da votação de utilizadores altamente satisfeitos a nível global - a ASUS permanece comprometida a proporcionar placas de som de topo ainda melhores para satisfazer os audiófilos ainda mais exigentes. Através dos anos de experiência no desenvolvimento da Essence One Essence STU e Essence III a Essence STX II oferece um design meticuloso uma performance quintessencial e uma musicalidade profunda — elementos que moldam o espírito de toda a série da Essence Hi-Fi.A Qualidade de áudio lendária acabou de ficar melhor - SNR de 124dB de topoA Essence STX II proporciona uma clareza de áudio de topo com 124dB de SNR uma qualidade invejável herdada da placa de som Essence STX revolucionária e amplamente elogiada — e até 64 vezes (64X) melhor que o hardware de áudio habitualmente incorporado nas motherboards. A saída dos auscultadores alcança uns fantásticos 120dB de SNR.Latência ultra-reduzidaUm relógio de elevada precisão é crucial para os audiófilos. Os circutios integrados são susceptíveis a calor e alterações de temperatura e é por isso que a Essence STX II inclui uma fonte de relógio com oscilador de compensação térmica de cristal (TCXO) de topo. É uma tecnologia de medição de tempo ultra-precisa que garante uma latência ultra-reduzida.Fonte de alimentação estável e consistenteA Essence STX II usa uma ligação de energia Molex com quatro pinos dedicada em vez de obter a sua energia a partir da ranhura de expansão como acontece com outras placas e isto significa um fornecimento de electricidade mais estável. O fornecimento de energia optimizado é garantido através de reguladores LDO (low-dropout) de alta fidelidade - sem precedentes na indústria das placas de som. Além disso os condensadores WIMA® bastante apreciados por audiófilos fornecem um som equilibrado.Op-Amps MUSESA musicalidade profunda que os ouvintes da Essence esperam é encapsulada pelos op-amps MUSES 8920 e MUSES 8820 que fornecem uma tonalidade realista e uma imagem de som espaçosa.7.1 Canais de som surround fáceis de adaptar e de personalizarExclusivo à Essence STX II 7.1 encontra-se uma daughterboard multicanal que proporciona 7.1 canais de som surround com saídas com 120dB de SNR de alta-fidelidade. Esta daughterboard fácil de encaixar encaixa-se numa ranhura adjacente à Essence STX II 7.1 por isso a instalação não podia ser mais conveniente. Cada canal é totalmente personalizável com nove ranhuras op-amp trocáveis — proporcionando aos audiófilos liberdade total para criarem a experiência de som surround perfeita para os seus ouvidos e ambientes auditivos.Amplificador de topo para auscultadoresO amplificador para auscultadores suporta até 600ohm de impedância — para que os audiófilos possam ligar os melhores auscultadores de elevada impedância para desfrutarem da qualidade pura fornecida pelo Essence STX II.Controlo de ganho para os auscultadoresOs engenheiros da ASUS equiparam a Essence STX II com um controlo de ganho adicional concebido especialmente para auscultadores IEM de alta sensibilidade que permitem aos músicos e puristas de áudio usar auscultadores que canalizam a saída de áudio directamente para o canal auditivo — isolando o ruído ambiente para uma audição que requer uma concentração sem perturbações.Três ranhuras op-amp trocáveisA Essence STX II beneficia de ranhuras op-amp trocáveis que permitem aos utilizadores criar timbres e combinações de tons diferentes.Kit de troca op-amp adicionalA Essence STX II até vem com um kit trocável que inclui três op-amps adicionais — dois Texas Instruments LME49720s e um MUSES 8820 — e um grampo que facilita a remoção dos microchips op-amp.Compatibilidade Bus: PCI ExpressPerformance Áudio:Relação Sinal-Ruído na Saída (Saída Frontal): 124 dBSinal para Ruído de saída (A-Weighted) (Saída para Auscultadores): 120 dBSinal para Ruído de entrada (A-Weighted) (Saída para Auscultadores): 118 dBSaída THD+N a 1kHz (Frontal): >0.0003 %(-110 dB)Saída THD+N a 1kHz (Headphones): >0.001 %(-100 dB)Frequência de Resposta (-3dB 16bit/44.1KHz entrada): 10 Hz até 90 KHzVoltagem de Escala Total: Vrms (Vp-p)Processador Áudio: ASUS AV100 High-Definition Sound Processor (Max. 192KHz/24bit)Digital-to-analog Converter(DAC): TI Bur-Brown PCM1792ATaxa de Amostragem e Resolução:Taxa de amostra e Resolução em Analógico: 44.1K/48K/96K/192KHz @ 16bit/24bitAnalog Recording Sample Através dos anos de experiência no desenvolvimento da Essence One Essence STU e Essence III a Essence STX II oferece um design meticuloso uma performance quintessencial e uma musicalidade profunda — elementos que moldam o espírito de toda a série da Essence Hi-Fi.A Qualidade de áudio lendária acabou de ficar melhor - SNR de 124dB de topoA Essence STX II proporciona uma clareza de áudio de topo com 124dB de SNR uma qualidade invejável herdada da placa de som Essence STX revolucionária e amplamente elogiada — e até 64 vezes (64X) melhor que o hardware de áudio habitualmente incorporado nas motherboards. A saída dos auscultadores alcança uns fantásticos 120dB de SNR.Latência ultra-reduzidaUm relógio de elevada precisão é crucial para os audiófilos. Os circutios integrados são susceptíveis a calor e alterações de temperatura e é por isso que a Essence STX II inclui uma fonte de relógio com oscilador de compensação térmica de cristal (TCXO) de topo. É uma tecnologia de medição de tempo ultra-precisa que garante uma latência ultra-reduzida.Fonte de alimentação estável e consistenteA Essence STX II usa uma ligação de energia Molex com quatro pinos dedicada em vez de obter a sua energia a partir da ranhura de expansão como acontece com outras placas e isto significa um fornecimento de electricidade mais estável. O fornecimento de energia optimizado é garantido através de reguladores LDO (low-dropout) de alta fidelidade - sem precedentes na indústria das placas de som. Além disso os condensadores WIMA® bastante apreciados por audiófilos fornecem um som equilibrado.Op-Amps MUSESA musicalidade profunda que os ouvintes da Essence esperam é encapsulada pelos op-amps MUSES 8920 e MUSES 8820 que fornecem uma tonalidade realista e uma imagem de som espaçosa.7.1 Canais de som surround fáceis de adaptar e de personalizarExclusivo à Essence STX II 7.1 encontra-se uma daughterboard multicanal que proporciona 7.1 canais de som surround com saídas com 120dB de SNR de alta-fidelidade. Esta daughterboard fácil de encaixar encaixa-se numa ranhura adjacente à Essence STX II 7.1 por isso a instalação não podia ser mais conveniente. Cada canal é totalmente personalizável com nove ranhuras op-amp trocáveis — proporcionando aos audiófilos liberdade total para criarem a experiência de som surround perfeita para os seus ouvidos e ambientes auditivos.Amplificador de topo para auscultadoresO amplificador para auscultadores suporta até 600ohm de impedância — para que os audiófilos possam ligar os melhores auscultadores de elevada impedância para desfrutarem da qualidade pura fornecida pelo Essence STX II.Controlo de ganho para os auscultadoresOs engenheiros da ASUS equiparam a Essence STX II com um controlo de ganho adicional concebido especialmente para auscultadores IEM de alta sensibilidade que permitem aos músicos e puristas de áudio usar auscultadores que canalizam a saída de áudio directamente para o canal auditivo — isolando o ruído ambiente para uma audição que requer uma concentração sem perturbações.Três ranhuras op-amp trocáveisA Essence STX II beneficia de ranhuras op-amp trocáveis que permitem aos utilizadores criar timbres e combinações de tons diferentes.Kit de troca op-amp adicionalA Essence STX II até vem com um kit trocável que inclui três op-amps adicionais — dois Texas Instruments LME49720s e um MUSES 8820 — e um grampo que facilita a remoção dos microchips op-amp.Compatibilidade Bus: PCI ExpressPerformance Áudio:Relação Sinal-Ruído na Saída (Saída Frontal): 124 dBSinal para Ruído de saída (A-Weighted) (Saída para Auscultadores): 120 dBSinal para Ruído de entrada (A-Weighted) (Saída para Auscultadores): 118 dBSaída THD+N a 1kHz (Frontal): >0.0003 %(-110 dB)Saída THD+N a 1kHz (Headphones): >0.001 %(-100 dB)Frequência de Resposta (-3dB 16bit/44.1KHz entrada): 10 Hz até 90 KHzVoltagem de Escala Total: Vrms (Vp-p)Processador Áudio: ASUS AV100 High-Definition Sound Processor (Max. 192KHz/24bit)Digital-to-analog Converter(DAC): TI Bur-Brown PCM1792ATaxa de Amostragem e Resolução:Taxa de amostra e Resolução em Analógico: 44.1K/48K/96K/192KHz @ 16bit/24bitAnalog Recording Sample description: "Add 3 external and 1 shared internal FireWire400 ports through a PCI slot. This 4 Port PCI IEEE 1394 FireWire 400 Adapter Card turns a motherboard PCI slot into four IEEE 1394a FireWire 6-pin female ports (1 internal, 3 external) - a cost-effective solution that lets you connect any FireWire 400 device that uses a 6-pin connector to your desktop computer.The card can be installed in either Mac or PC computers, providing a practical solution for connecting iPods, MP3 players, portable drives, digital camcorders and more. The adapter card supports hot-swappable connectivity, allowing you to plug, unplug, and swap your FireWire peripherals with ease, saving time and hassle.The 4 port FireWire PCI adapter card includes a copy of ULEAD's VideoStudio SE Basic video editing software, making it easy to capture and edit video from your digital video camcorder."

title: "Verbatim UltraLife Gold Archival Grade - CD-R x 5 700 MB storage media" " Verbatim media 96319 CD-ROM Media CDW.com
description: "Verbatim's proprietary dual reflective technology is comprised of a silver layer for broad compatibility and a gold layer for long archival life. The highly reflective silver layer allows the UltraLife CD-R disc to look like a standard silver disc to CD burners. This feature provides a low initial error rate, important for long archival life, and the same drive read/write compatibility as standard silver-only discs.The gold reflective layer is naturally resistant to corrosion. The gold layer overlaps the silver layer and prevents oxygen from coming through the lacquer layer or edge of the disc and corroding the silver. Silver oxidation can be a primary factor which limits the lifetime of CD media."

title: "StarTech.com DisplayPort to DVI Dual Link Active Adapter Converter - DP DVI-D 2560x1600 3D support"@en-US "Audio & Video Accessories Page 481 | Home Entertainment Centers Online"@en-US
description: "The DP2DVID2 DisplayPort   to DVI (Dual-Link) Adapter actively converts the output signal from a DisplayPort video source for use with a DVI-D display (monitor, etc.) or projector, helping to eliminate the equipment costs of upgrading a DVI display to a newer model for the sake of compatibility.  The adapter supports high resolution video (up to 2560x1600 at 60Hz), maintaining the outstanding graphical performance from a DisplayPort-equipped desktop video card, laptop or MacBook  .  DP2DVID2 performs an active DisplayPort-DVI conversion that is suitable for video sources that output either multimode (DP++) or single-mode DisplayPort signals. This ensures the adapter can be used even with graphics cards that aren't capable of outputting multimode DP++ signals, such as ATI   Eyefinity cards.  Back by StarTech.com 2-year warranty, with free lifetime technical support."@en-US

title: "Samsung - DDR4 8 GB DIMM 288-pin" " Samsung 288-pin M393A1G40DB0-CPB System Memory (RAM) CDW.com
description: "Samsung DDR4 is an optimized solution for highly virtualized environments, high-performance computing and networking.Achieving bandwidth speeds up to 3.2Gbps, Samsung DDR4 delivers higher performance at a higher speed than both DDR2 and DDR3. Compared to DDR3L (low power DDR3), Samsung DDR4 shows an overall improvement in performance in every DIMM and a performance that is more than 40 percent better at 1 DIMM per channel.A major decrease in voltage and the improved I/O power efficiency of DDR4 synchronous dynamic RAM (SDRAM) translates into significant cost savings. According to Samsung internal testing, DDR4 boasts a continuous working voltage of 1.2 V, a voltage that is 11 percent lower than the 1.35 V consumed by DDR3L. By adopting POD (Pseudo Open Drain) for data transmission, Samsung DDR4's input/output (I/O) power consumption is reduced by 50 percent compared to the previously-used SSTL (Stub Series Terminated Logic) of DDR3L. Overall, Samsung DDR4 shows a Performance/watt level more than 20 percent higher than DDR3L."

title: "Olympus Stylus Tough TG-Tracker Action Camera (Green) "@en Aden " Olympus | Digital SLR Cameras Toronto Canada Store
description:
"
                        At first glance, the all new Olympus TG-Tracker looks rugged and compact, easy to carry and easy to shoot. But there's far more here than meets the eye. That's because TG-Tracker is part of the Olympus Tough Family - worry-free cameras built to handle abuse so you can concentrate on getting great shots. TG-Tracker is waterproof to depths of 100 ft (30m), crushproof up to 220 lbf (100kgf), shockproof from 7ft (2.1m), freezeproof to 14F (-10C), and dustproof. Most other action cams need protective housings. That means more stuff to carry around, clumsy camera operation, and a difficult time capturing sound. With TG-Tracker, no housing equals better overall performance.
For adventurers looking to analyze their activities, switch the TG-Tracker to LOG mode to record the data from the camera's built-in GPS, compass, accelerometer, thermometer, and barometer. The location data from these sensors, such as location, altitude, direction, and temperature, can be viewed on the camera's monitor and downloaded for later use with the Olympus Image Track (OI.Track) mobile app.
 Main Features 

UHD 4K Video at 30 fps
Maximum Lens Aperture: F2
1080p at 60 fps / 720p at 120 fps
8MP Photos
204deg Lens
Waterproof to 98.4' / Shockproof to 7'
Freezeproof to 14F (-10C)
Built-In LED Headlamp
Tilt-Out 1.5" LCD
Built-In Sensors Track Location/Movement
View Data Logs via OI.Track Mobile App
Recording Media: microSD/HC/XC
Unit Dimensions (WxHxD): 1.4 x 2.2 x 3.7" / 35.0 x 56.5 x 93.2mm
Unit Weight: 6.35 oz / 180 g including battery and card

 What's in the box

Lens Protector

Joint Screw
Mount Coupling
Steady Grip

description: "Clone or Erase 2.5in/3.5in SATA hard drives, without a host computer connection. The below list of StarTech.com adapters have been specifically tested, to ensure compatibility with this drive duplicator: 2.5/3.5in IDE drives - SAT2IDEADP; mSATA drives - SAT2MSAT25; M.2 (NGFF) drives - SAT32M225."

title: "STARTECH.COM SV231DPDDUA 2 Port Dual DisplayPort USB KVM Switch with Audio" "Startech.Com Sv231dpddua Displayport"
description:
"OverviewThe SV231DPDDUA 2-Port USB Dual DisplayPort KVM Switch combines the next generation of digital display interface standards with seamless USB KVM control of connected PC or Mac computers. The world''s first Dual Monitor DisplayPort KVM switch allows you to switch between two high-end machines, with dual head or twin DisplayPort video cards in each. The switch can also provide the ideal solution for computers with a single DisplayPort video out, and a second video source such as DVI, using a low cost accessory adapter. Delivering ideal multi-computer control for demanding high-resolution multimedia applications, or computer environments requiring true high definition capability, the robust KVM switch supports Dual DisplayPort connections with native resolutions of 2560 x 1600 (@60 Hz, 30 bpp), as well as 2-channel stereo audio and microphone input. Suitable for applications that utilize high quality static imaging, such as medical/health care applications (MRI, X-ray diagnostics etc.), the KVM switch supports a maximum resolution of 3840 x 2400 at a reduced refresh rate. "STARTECH.COM SV231DPDDUA 2 Port Dual DisplayPort USB KVM Switch with Audio" "Startech.Com Sv231dpddua Displayport" "OverviewThe SV231DPDDUA 2-Port USB Dual DisplayPort KVM Switch combines the next generation of digital display interface standards with seamless USB KVM control of connected PC or Mac computers. The world''s first Dual Monitor DisplayPort KVM switch allows you to switch between two high-end machines, with dual head or twin DisplayPort video cards in each. The switch can also provide the ideal solution for computers with a single DisplayPort video out, and a second video source such as DVI, using a low cost accessory adapter. Delivering ideal multi-computer control for demanding high-resolution multimedia applications, or computer environments requiring true high definition capability, the robust KVM switch supports Dual DisplayPort connections with native resolutions of 2560 x 1600 (@60 Hz, 30 bpp), as well as 2-channel stereo audio and microphone input. Suitable for applications that utilize high quality static imaging, such as medical/health care applications (MRI, X-ray diagnostics etc.), the KVM switch supports a maximum resolution of 3840 x 2400 at a reduced refresh rate. description:
"

Den Hüftgurt kaufen sie bitte gesondert, hier bei uns.
Maße (H/B/T): S: ca. 53 cm / 28 cm / 24 cm M: ca. 58 cm / 28 cm / 26 cm L: ca. 63 cm / 28 cm / 28 cm XL: 66 cm /  28 cm / 30 cm

"@de, "
Hauptfach: 100d Robic High Tensil Strength NylonVerstärkungen: 200d Robic High Tensil Strength Nylongering beanspruchte Flächen: 70d SilNylon, SI-beschichtet, 100% NylonMesh: Power mesh und Air mesh Pad: EVA Schaum
"@de, "
Der Gossamer Gear Gorilla 40 Rucksack ist der richtige Leichtrucksack für Grammjäger mit superultraleichter Ausrüstung auf langen Touren. Für Wanderer auf leichten schnellen Touren über mehrere Tage ist es der perfekte Allrounder. Durch Kompressionsgurte kann die Ladung bei nicht vollem Rucksack schön dicht an den Rücken geholt werden. Das macht den Gorilla selbst für Tagesausflüge oder Wochenendtouren zu einem sehr flexiblen Begleiter. Wer nicht so viel Ausrüstung verstauen muss und einige Tage wandern geht, ist mit dem Packvolumen des Gorilla gut beraten. Das Hauptfach fasst 29 L, in die Aussentaschen passen nochmal 11 Liter rein. Das Hauptfach ist mit ca. 7 L erweiterbar, gedacht für Resupply oder Lebensmitteleinkäufe unterwegs.  Wir liefern den überarbeiteten Leichtrucksack ohne Hüftgurt aus. (Den Hüftgurt kaufen sie bitte gesondert, hier bei uns.) Dieser neuere Hüftgurt ist noch ergonomischer und besser gepolstert. Die Zip-Taschen sind nun fest integriert. Das Tragegestell besteht aus einem Aluminium-Rahmen in Form eines umgedrehten U, kurz Stay genannt. Der Stay überträgt die Last direkt auf den Hüftgurt. Er läuft unsichbar im Bodenbereich aus dem Rucksack raus in 2 Aufnahmetaschen im Hüftgurt. Der Hüftgurt überträgt die Last direkt auf die Hüfte. Bis zu 14 kg werden so komfortabel gemeistert. Die Schultergurte sind sehr komfortabel konstruiert, für Frauen und Männer gleichermaßen.Die Fronttasche ist klassisch aus stabilem Mesh mit Ripstop-Nylon-Boden. Es ist groß genug um nasse Tarps oder Zelte zu verstauen. Auf der Rucksack-Rückenseite befindet sich der Powermesh Mattenhalter. Er nimmt die im Lieferumfang befindliche kleine Isomatte auf. Entnommen dienst sie zusätzlich als Sitzkissen, am Rucksack dient sie als Rückenpolster. Wer Hüftgurt und Pad nicht braucht, spart auch hier Gewicht ein. Das Hauptfach-Gewebe besteht aus dem neuen 100d Robic Nylon. Der Boden ist verstärkt, teils wird sogar 200d Robic eingesetzt an beanspruchten Stellen. Mäßig belastete Bereiche sind aus Silnylon gerfertigt. Je nach Beldung kann mit den Seitenkompressionsriemen die Ladung stabilisiert werden. Auch der Gorilla 40 Ruksack hat das bewährte OTT(TM) (Over-the-Top) Deckel-Verschluss-System. Es sorgt für einen sicheren Verschluss des Rucksacks und hat eine Zip-Tasche. Halterungen für Trekkingstöcker, Eisaxt, Trinkschlauch, Trinkblase, ein abnehmbarer Brustgurt und weitere diverse Laschen sind montiert. Die beiden Seitentaschen können mit Trinkflaschen bestückt werden. Cool ist, man muss den Rucksack nicht absetzen um diese unterwegs zu entnehmen. *Im Lieferumfang befinden sich nur der Rucksack. Den Hüftgurt kaufen sie bitte gesondert, hier bei uns.
"@de, "

ultraleichter, Tourenrucksack mit 40 L
top Lastübertragung da Tragegestell direkt und flexibel mit Hüftgurt verbunden
neuer, ergonomischerer Hüftgurt mit Zip-Pockets (muss gesondert gekauft werden)
neue, bequemere Unisex-Form der Schultergurte für Frauen und Männer
sehr stabiles Robic 100d Nylon
Seitenkompressionsriemen
2 Seitentaschen, Fronttasche aus Mesh
die Seitentaschen sind gut Wasserflasche, da erreichbar ohne den Rucksack abzusetzen
Deckeltasche mit Zip-Fach
Schlauchport, Trinkblasenhalterschlaufe, Schlauchhalter an den Schultergurten
Schlaufen für Trekkingstöcker, Eisäxte

Rückenpad ist gleichzeitig Frame und Sitzkissen
Hauptfach mit ca. 7 L erweiterbar, gedacht für Resupply oder Lebensmitteleinkäufe unterwegs
"@de

title: "Tripp Lite 750VA 450W UPS Eco Green Battery Back Up Compact 120V USB RJ11" " Tripp RJ11 - ECO750UPS UPS/Battery Backups CDW.com
description: "This product is ENERGY STAR qualified for its ability to save customers money while helping to protect the environment. The ECO750UPS standby green UPS offers complete protection from blackouts, brownouts and transient surges. Supports green energy savings via built-in ECO outlets that automatically power off unused computer accessories like printers or multi-media speakers when the computer is not in use. Full load efficiency rating of 99% also offers energy-savings and cooler operation by limiting UPS power consumption to less than 5 watts! Eco-friendly design meets strict RoHS environmental standards.  How the Energy-Saving Feature Works:Green Outletâ¢ technology saves up to $50 on annual energy bills by cutting power to designated energy-saving outlets when the master device (e.g. TV, computer) is turned off, preventing idle devices from wasting energy. Other outlets remain powered to support devices that operate continuously, such as DVRs, routers and broadband modems. Provides uninterrupted transition to battery-derived AC output during brownouts and power failures with enough runtime to save and shutdown connected equipment without data loss. Offers complete protection in an ultra-compact desktop or wall-mountable housing. Includes 6 battery supported outlets for computer, monitor and four vital system peripherals, plus 6 additional surge suppression-only outlets for accessories not requiring battery support. USB port enables UPS configuration options and unattended system shutdown without data loss in the case of extended power failure.  PowerAlert software is available via free download from the Tripp Lite website. USB cable included. Built-in single line RJ11 phone suppression protects modem, fax machine, cordless phone or other accessories with a dialup/DSL phone connection. Built-in audible alarm and front panel LEDs offer continuous status information regarding line and battery power operation. 750VA/450 watt power handling ability supports entry-level PC systems for up to 45 minutes during power fail conditions. $100,000 connected equipment insurance (USA, Puerto Rico, & Canada Only). â¢750VA power saving, ultra-compact GREEN UPS â¢99% line-mode efficiency saves energy and operating costs â¢4 built-in "ECO" outlets save power by automatically turning off connected accessories when the computer is not in use â¢Includes HID-compliant USB port, single line TEL / DSL line surge suppression, space saving right-angle input plug and six surge-only outlets â¢Input: NEMA 5-15P (120V 15A) / Output: 12 NEMA 5-15R (120V) â¢3 year product warranty / $100,000 Ultimate Lifetime Insurance"

title: "AFINIA H480 Desktop 3D Printer" " AFINIA Printer - Printers CDW.com
description: "AFINIA H480The AFINIA H480 3D Printer provides a true "Plug and Play" 3D printing experience. The AFINIA 3D Printer comes fully assembled with easy to install software for both the PC and Mac. The 3D printer can prototype a part or model that is up to 5 inches cubed in size with layer thickness ranging from .40mm down to .15mm for incredible accuracy. A heated build platform aids in the adhesion of your model and greatly decreases the chance of warping as the ABS cools.AWARD WINNINGMAKE Magazine awarded the AFINIA H-Series âBest Overall Experienceâ with âEasiest Setupâ and âEasiest to Useâ in their 2013 3D Printing Buyerâs Guide. Now with new setup features, the Easiest just got Easier!CNET awarded the AFINIA H-Series 4 out of 5 stars with this quote from Rich Brown, Senior Editor âThe AFINIA H-Series Desktop 3D printer is the most approachable model weâve reviewed, and we recommend it to anyone serious about getting started with 3D printing.âAUTO-LEVELING AND NOZZLE HEIGHTThe H480 features Auto-Leveling Platform Calibration and Nozzle Height Detection which makes the printer setup quick and easy.EASY TO USEThe included 3D printing software features an easy-to-use interface to import .STL files and automatically generate any support material needed for your design. This support material, layer thickness, and fill can be optimized in the software for more intricate builds. The breakaway support material is easily removed by hand or with the included set of tools. Design files for 3D printing can be created using a multitude of free, entry level or professional CAD/CAM software such as Autodesk, Solidworks, Sketchup, Tinkercad, Blender and openSCAD. There is also an extensive online community for downloading and sharing 3D model files.STANDALONE PRINTINGThe AFINIA H480 3D printer comes equipped with built-in, on-board memory so once a job has been transferred to the printer, it is no longer necessary to have it connected to your computer.USE NON-PROPRIETARY 1.75mm ABS or PLA PLASTIC FILAMENTThe H480 prints using inexpensive, non-proprietary, high-quality plastic filament. title: "Apple - Smart Keyboard for 12.9 Inch iPad Pro Gray"@en-US
description: "Smart Keyboard available at Best BuyThe new Smart Keyboard for iPad Pro has all the utility of an ordinary full-size keyboard, but its technology is far from conventional. The entire keyboard is draped with a custom-woven fabric that has been laser ablated to precisely define each key and ensure a satisfyingly fast and natural key feel. Below the surface of Smart Keyboard is a new conductive material. At just 0.1mm, it is nearly as thin as a piece of paper, yet strong enough to withstand a lifetime of folding. And it's why you won't find any batteries, cord or on/off switches with Smart Keyboard."@en-US

title: "Gigabyte BRIX GB-BKi7HA-7500 (rev. 1.0) - Ultra Compact PC Kit Core i7 75" " Gigabyte 75 GB-BKI7HA-7500 Desktop Computers CDWG.com
description: "Challenging the essence of how a desktop PC is defined, GIGABYTE engineers have developed an ultra-compact PC with a brushed aluminum surface chassis design. Ideal for a broad range of computing applications at home or in the office, the BRIX expounds sheer simplicity and convenience.The latest USB 3.1 offers a staggering 10 Gb/s transfer speed, 2x faster than USB 3.0 and backward compatibility with existing USB devices.GIGABYTE ensures users won't be limited by the standards or connections on the BRIX, by including HDMI 2.0 and support for HDCP 2.2 users can rest assured that their device will be able to display content to its full potential. title: "Ultimate LPT1000QR Hyperstation QR Laptop Stand"@en Stand | PSSL"@en
description:
"  Ultimate LPT1000QR Hyperstation QR Laptop or Equipment 
Stand
The all-new HyperStation QR is a dynamic laptop stand for the working DJ and 
traveling musician. The HyperStation QR features angle-adjustable telescoping 
support arms that support laptops, small mixers, groove production electronics, 
drum pad controllers, and more and has a height-adjustable second tier. Mobile 
music production demands both portability and durability and the HyperStation QR 
delivers on both accounts. It folds down flat as one piece, fitting into just 
about any gig bag or backpack while being far more durable than typical wire 
frame laptop stands.
QuickRelease (QR) Center PostWhat makes the HyperStation 
QR different from all other laptop stands is the patented QuickRelease center 
post, which gives you three stand possibilities. Quickly and easily, you can 
release the support arms and center post of the HyperStation QR and mount it to 
a mic stand or one of the Ultimate Support APEX AX-48 Pro keyboard stands! 
Within seconds, you can move your laptop to a mic stand and back into the 
HyperStation QR base without ever dismounting it from the support arms! What's 
more, Ultimate Support has included a small T-stand adapter that fits in the 
bottom of the center post so you can set it on a desktop without the 
HyperStation QR base. So, you can use your laptop with the HyperStation QR on 
its base, with it's support arms and center post on a 5/8" threaded stand (such 
as a mic stand), or on an included T-stand adapter on a desktop!
Portable ProductionHyperStation QR is designed to go 
wherever your music takes you. While sturdy enough to safely hold your laptop 
and other small electronics, it folds up as one piece and fits in a backpack! 
Fold it up when you're on the go; set it up when you're ready to play.
Secure and SturdyDon't let the sleek styling fool you, 
this is not a flimsy, plastic stand! HyperStation QR is constructed from 
die-cast aluminum making it incredibly sturdy and surprisingly light. 
HyperStation QR features patent-pending technology that truly locks it upright 
when you're ready to make music. Plus, you don't have to worry about your laptop 
falling off. Simply place your laptop at whatever angle suits your need and 
secure it in place with the telescoping, non-marring arm stops!
Second Tier and More!The modern musician and DJ artist 
carries additional hard drives, MP3 players, USB hubs, audio interfaces, and 
other computer accessories with them to each and every gig. HyperStation QR has 
you covered with a second tier that is height adjustable and fitted with ports 
for venting. HyperStation also ships with a handy carrying pouch for protective 
transport and cable management clips to keep cables out of the way.
Ultimate Support HyperStation Features:

  QuickRelease center post provides fast mounting to and from the 
  HyperStation QR and a 5/8" threaded post (mic stand, etc.) 
  T-stand included for third mounting option 
  Angle-adjustable telescoping support arms that lock laptop in place 
  Locks in setup position for stability 
  Constructed from die-cast aluminum making it incredibly sturdy 
  Folds down flat 
 …  More        "@en

The SV231DPDDUA 2-Port USB Dual DisplayPort KVM Switch with Audio and USB 2.0 Hub combines next generation digital display standards with seamless KVM control, allowing you to switch between 2 dual head or twin DisplayPort systems. Also ideal for systems with a single DisplayPort output, and a second video source such as DVI or HDMI, using a low cost accessory adapter.Delivering multi-computer control for high-res multimedia applications, the dual view KVM supports resolutions of 2560x1600 (@60 Hz) with DisplayPort HD audio, as well as 2-channel analog stereo audio and microphone input.Suitable for high quality static imaging, such as medical applications (MRI, X-ray, etc.), a maximum resolution of 3840x2400 is supported at reduced refresh rates."

description: "NVIDIA Quadro K1200 - Incredible 3D application performance in a flexible form factor. Now included in the box, a full-height bracket lets this single-slot and low-profile board fit into any full-height (ATX) desktop, mid-tower, or desk side tower enclosure. Four mini-DisplayPort to DVI-D SL adapters are included to enable DVI or DisplayPort displays to be driven out of the box (four displays active simultaneously). The Quadro K1200 is the perfect choice for Manufacturing or Media & Entertainment professionals who are transitioning to 4K applications, workflows, and photorealistic HDR (High Dynamic Range) rendering enabled by NVIDIA Iray. 512 CUDA cores and 4 GB of GDDR5 GPU memory with fast bandwidth enables your customers to create large, complex 3D models, and an all-new display engine drives up to four displays natively with DisplayPort 1.2 support for true 4K resolutions like 3840 x 2160 at 60 Hz with 30-bit color. Designed and built specifically for professional workstations, NVIDIA Quadro GPUs power more than 100+ professional applications across a broad range of industries including manufacturing, media and entertainment, sciences, and energy. Professionals trust them to realize their most ambitious visions - whether its product design, visualization and simulation, or spectacular visual storytelling - and get results to market faster. PNY provides unsurpassed service and commitment to its professional graphics customers offering: pre and post-sales support, dedicated Quadro Field Application engineers and direct tech support hot lines. In addition, PNY delivers a complete solution including the appropriate adapters, cables, brackets, software installation disc and documentation to ensure a quick and successful install."

title: " Universal Audio Apollo 16 v2 "@en "Universal Reviews & Prices | Equipboard®"@en
description:
"
                16 channels of premium audio with realtime UAD plug-in power.

The new Apollo 16 is an elegant update to UA' premium audio interface ” delivering enhanced sound with the tone, feel, and flow of analog recording. Perfect for professional studios, this 18 x 20 Thunderbolt interface offers twice the analog connectivity of the Apollo 8/8p, making it ideal for pairing with mixing consoles and outboard processors.  

Apollo 16 further distinguishes itself with Realtime UAD Processing, letting you record at near-zero latency through the full range of UAD plug-ins from Neve, Studer, Manley, Lexicon, and more. Apollo Expanded software now allows cascading up to four Apollos and six total UAD-2 devices in a single system over Thunderbolt (Mac), so you can scale up your studio as your needs grow.  

With its powerful onboard UAD-2 QUAD processing, genuine UA analog design, and next-generation A/D and D/A conversion, Apollo 16 puts class-leading audio performance in a sleek new package.  

Next-Generation Apollo A/D and D/A Conversion
Apollo 16 improves upon the original Apollo' gold-standard audio quality with completely redesigned, class-leading digital conversion ” giving you increased dynamic range and even lower THD. This results in breathtaking clarity, depth, and accuracy in your recordings, from tracking and overdubbing, to mixing and mastering.  

Realtime UAD Plug-In Processing for Tracking, Mixing, and Mastering
While Apollo 16' œnatural sound is very open and transparent, it can quickly deliver a stunning range of classic analog tones and color via its Realtime UAD Processing. Available with generous UAD-2 QUAD processing onboard, Apollo' DSP Acceleration allows for recording through UAD Powered Plug-Ins ” with as low as sub-2ms latency ” letting you monitor and œprint audio using classic analog emulations from Ampex, Lexicon, Manley, Neve, Roland, SSL, Studer, and more.  

The Apollo 16' bundled œRealtime Analog Classics Plus suite of UAD plug-ins gives you the UA 610-B Tube Preamp & EQ, Raw Distortion, Softube Amp Rooms, legacy LA-2A, 1176, and Fairchild compressors, Pultec EQs, and more, so you have a rack full of bonafide audio classics, right out of the box.  

Using Apollo, UAD plug-ins are also available during mixing and mastering, putting UAD plug-ins (VST, RTAS, AU, AAX 64) at your disposal throughout the creative process.  

Apollo Expanded and Console 2.0
Thanks to Apollo Expanded software, users of Thunderbolt-equipped Apollo Twin, Apollo 8, Apollo 8p, and Apollo 16 audio interfaces can combine up to four Apollos and six total UAD-2 devices ” adding I/O and DSP as their studio grows. Apollo Expanded also provides seamless integration with previous generation Apollos over Thunderbolt.  

With Apollo 16' Console 2.0 application ” a complete re-imagining of Apollo' original Console software ” you can take advantage of over 25 user-requested features such as Channel Strip presets, Drag & Drop functionality, dynamically resizable windows, and more.  

*All trademarks are recognized as property of their respective owners. Individual UAD Powered Plug-Ins sold separately.

              "@en

description: "Vengeance LPX memory is designed for high-performance overclocking. The heat spreader is made of pure aluminum for faster heat dissipation, and the eight-layer PCB helps manage heat and provides superior overclocking headroom. Each IC is individually screened for performance potential. The DDR4 form factor is optimized for the latest Intel X99 and 100 Series motherboards and offers higher frequencies, greater bandwidth, and lower power consumption than DDR3 modules. Vengeance LPX DDR4 modules are compatibility-tested across X99 and 100 Series motherboards for reliably fast performance. There's XMP 2.0 support for trouble-free automatic overclocking. And, they're available in multiple colors to match your motherboard, your components, or just your style. Customer Service / Tech support: 1-888-222-4346 opt. 1"

title: "Korg electribe 2SRD Music Production Sampler"@en Sampler | PSSL"@en
description:
"  Korg Electribe 2SRD Music Production Sampler

The Electribe sampler is a sample-based production machine that lets you construct beats at maximum speed. You can freely edit and resample using waveforms that you've loaded and preset samples. Modulation and effects can be controlled easily just by turning knobs on the top panel. In addition, a variety of input interfaces optimized for inputting rhythm, bass, or melody allow you to smoothly create sequences as fast as you can think. The sequences that you create can then undergo additional evolution on stage or in your laptop. You can enjoy intuitive live performances that link various devices with the Electribe sampler, or utilize this capability for full-fledged music production by exporting sequence data to Ableton Live for detailed editing and final mixing. 

The latest system version 2 adds a much-requested pattern chain function that will be a great asset for live performances or music production. The lineup has also become more colorful with the new metallic red model. And we've also provided bonus patterns that reveal even greater sonic potential. Making your beat-making ideas rapidly take shape. It's the Electribe sampler; a sampler + sequencer that's thoroughly optimized for speed.

Features:

    Effortless knob-based sample shaping
    Import any waveform and resample
    High-quality preset samples that let your ideas take shape quickly
    Modulation section for quick access to dramatic sound-shaping parameters
    A wide selection of insert effects add the final touch to parts and patterns
    Control your sequences in real time with absolute freedom
    Use Pattern Set and Pattern Chain to build and organize full arrangements
    X/Y pad offers real-time effects performance
    Sync, MIDI, and Audio In jacks for integration into any setup



Specifications:

Sound System

    Type: PCM sound engine + analog modeling sound engine
    Maximum polyphony: 24 voices
    Sample: type (920), pitch/glide, edit
    Sample types: analog (16), audio in (2), kick (37), snare (44), clap (12), hihat (37), cymbal (8), hits (33), shots (44), voice (31), SE (7), FX (30), tom (10), percussion (31), phrase (15), loop (22), PCM (31), user sample (499) Filter: filter (cutoff), resonance, EG Int, LPF/HPF/BPF (3)
    Modulation type: (72), depth, speed
    Amp/Envelope generator: level, pan, attack, decay/release, amp EG on/off
    Scale types: 35
    Gate arpeggiator types: 50
    Sampling frequency: 48 kHz
    AD/DA conversion: 24 bit sampler
    User samples: up to 499 samples
    Memory total: maximum approximately 270 seconds
    Edits: start/end point, loop start point, tune, time slice, level, direction, resampling effect
    Insert effect: one unit (can be used on each of the 16 parts), type (38), edit, insert FX on/off
    Master effect: one unit, type (32), touch pad, master FX on/off, master fx hold on/off sequencer
    Number of steps: 16 steps x 4 number of parts 16 parts
    Number of patterns: 250 patterns (150 presets / 100 initial)
    Motion sequences: up to 24 motion sequences can be stored (for each pattern)
    Groove types: 25
    Pattern set: up to 64 patterns can be stored
    Pattern chain: up to 250 patterns can be chained
    Export: Ableton Live project file format, WAV file format (48 kHz, 16 bit)
    Event recording: up to 100 files can be saved


Trigger Pads

    Number of pads: 16 pads (velocity sensitive)
    Modes trigger, sequencer, keyboard, chord, step jump, pattern set


Touch Pad

    Modes: gate arp, touch scale, master FX


Connectors

    Audio: L/Mono, R output (standard phone jack), headphones (stereo mini jack), audio input (stereo mini jack)
    MIDI: in, out (use an included MIDI adapter cable)
    USB: type micro B
    Sync: in, out (stereo mini jack)


External Storage Device

    SD card (512 MB - 2 GB), SDHC card (Up to 32 GB)


Additional Specifications

    Power supply: AC adapter (DC 9V) or AA battery x 6
    Battery life: approximately 5 hours
    Current consumption: less than 500 mA
    Chassis: zinc die cast
    Dimensions: 13.35” x 7.44” x 1.77” (WxDxH)
    Weight: 3.53 Lbs./1.6 kg
    Included items: AC adapter (DC9V), MIDI adapter cable x 2, Ableton Live 9 lite (license card included)
 …  More        "@en

title: "HPE Light Endurance Enterprise - solid state drive 960 GB SATA 6G" " HPE 6G 756601-B21 Solid State Drives (SSDs) CDW.com
description: "Do you need more performance from your HPE ProLiant Server series or HPE Synergy platforms? HPE Solid State Drives (SSDs) deliver exceptional performance and endurance while reducing power consumption for customers with applications requiring high random read and write IOPs performance. Categorized by Read Intensive (RI), Mixed Use (MU), and Write Intensive (WI), you can choose the right SSD that tailors to your workload demands. Also, you can prevent data loss and monitor the SSD life with HPE SmartSSD Wear Gauge compatibility in management tools. Leveraging NAND Flash technology, they support HPE ProLiant servers including Gen9 and server storage platforms. Available as Small Form Factor (SFF) and Large Form Factor (LFF) hot plug devices, non-hot plug SFF devices, and SFF Quick Release devices, you have great flexibility in your installation. These drives deliver higher performance, better latency, and more power-efficient solutions when compared with traditional rotating media."

title: "WD 6TB Red 3,5" SATA III 6Gbit/s IntelliPower 64MB Cache NAS 7/24 (WD60EFRX)"@tr 5" 3
description:
"


  

 

 

WD Red büyümekte

Başarı formülümüz, WD Red'in mümkün olan en yüksek kapasitelere çıkışını sağllamıştır. 6 TB'a kadar kapasite sunan WD, toplam 1 ile 16 arasında değişen yuva ile müşterilerimiz için çok daha geniş ve daha kapsamlı NAS çözüm yelpazesi sunmaktadır. WD Red ailesi büyümekte.






NASware, 3.0'a büyümüştür

En iyi NAS deneyimini sunma kararlılığımızı yansıtacak şekilde tasarlanmış olan NASware 3.0, 6 ile 8 arası NAS yuvası için ek destek ile NAS ortamı için WD Red'i daha da optimize hale getirerek verdiğimiz sözü pekiştirmektedir. WD Red artık NASware 3.0. sayesinde 1 ile 8 yuvalı küçük NAS sistemlerini destekliyor ve böylelikle sürücü uyumluluğunu ve güvenilirliğini de arttırmış oluyor. 8 yuvalı bir sistemde toplam 48 TB'a kadar kapasite sunan WD Red daha yeni bir nesil NAS deneyimidir.






 

Profesyonel çözümler

Özellikle SMB müşterileri düşünülerek tasarlanan WD Red ailesi WD Red Pro'nun da katılımıyla daha da genişledi. WD Red Pro 8-16 yuvalı, orta ve geniş ölçekli NAS ortamlarında mevcuttur. Artan iş yükünüze destek olmak için tasarlanan 4 TB'a kadar kapasite sunan WD Red Pro size 5 yıllık sınırlı garanti sunuyor.


        


NAS'da test edildi

İz bırakan, üstün teknolojisi ile WD Red, piyasada bulabileceğiniz en kapsamlı NAS ortağı uyumlu sabit sürücüdür.* Bu, herhangi bir
NAS kasası satın aldığınızda sizin için en uygun sürücünün WD Red olacağından kesinlikle emin olabileceğiniz anlamına gelir. 
Ürünümüzle gurur duyuyoruz ve vizyonumuzu müşterilerimizle paylaşıyoruz.

*Nisan 2014 itibari ile üretilen ürünleri yansıtan veriler.

      

Ev kullanımı için NAS

WD Red sabit sürücülerle donatılmış NAS sistemleri ile, bağlı ev ortamınızı bir üst seviyeye taşıyın ve medya aktarmanın, bilgisayarlarınızı yedeklemenin, dosya paylaşımı yapmanın ve dijital içeriklerinizi daha hızlı ve daha kolay bir şekilde yönetmenin keyfini çıkarın. 
Uyumluluğu arttırılmış WD Red NASware 3.0 deneyimi ile mobil cihazlar, bilgisayar, TV, stereo ve diğer araçlarınızdan paylaşım yapmak 
çok keyifli.  WD Red, kendi güvenilir Kişisel Bulutunuzu yaratmanızı sağlar.

Küçük işletmeler için NAS

1 ila 8 yuvalı NAS sisteminiz için üretilmiş olan WD Red sabit sürücülerle küçük çaplı işletmelerinizin etkinliğini ve verimliliğini arttırın. 
WD Red, mevcut ağ alt yapınızla sorunsuz entegrasyon sağlayan ve sistem uyumluluğunu arttıran NASware 3.0 ile birlikte temin edilir. 
WD Red NAS sabit sürücülerle, çalışanlarınıza dosyalarını hızlıca paylaşma ve klasörlerini güvenli bir şekilde NAS çözümlerine yedekleme 
imkanı vererek işletmenize değer katın. 8 ila 16 yuvalı olan orta ile büyük işletme ortamları için, WD Red Pro kullanın.
                                                                       

Özel NASware 3.0 Teknolojisi

Özel NASware 3.0 teknolojimiz WD Red'in zorlu küçük NAS ortamında yüksek performansla çalışmasını sağlar. NAS sisteminize WD Red ekleyerek sadece etkinliği ve güvenilirliği arttırmakla kalmaz, aynı zamanda en iyi NAS deneyimini de yaşarsınız.
3D Active Balance Plus

Geliştirilmiş ikili düzlem denge kontrol teknolojimiz, genel sürücü performansında ve güvenilirliğinde çarpıcı bir artış sağlar. Uygun biçimde dengelenmeyen sabit sürücüler, çok sürücülü sistemlerde aşırı titreşime ve gürültüye, sabit sürücünün ömrünün azalmasına ve zaman içinde performansın düşmesine sebep olabilir.

Doğru Seçim!

WD Red, ev ve küçük ofis NAS sistemleri ile RAID özellikli PC'ler için özel olarak tasarlanan bir sabit sürücüdür.
Artırılmış Güvenilirlik

NAS sistemleriniz hep açık kaldığı için, son derece güvenilir bir sürücünün olması çok önemlidir. Standart sabit sürücülere göre %35 MTBF iyileşmesi ile, NASware 3.0'a sahip WD Red sürücü, 7/24 çalışan ortamlar için tasarlanmıştır.

NAS Uyumluluğu

Tüm WD Red sürücülerde yer alan gelişmiş ürün yazılım teknolojisi NASware 3.0, sorunsuz entegrasyon, sağlam veri koruması ve NAS ve RAID ortamlarında kullanılan sistemler için ideal performans sağlar.





Buradaki Sır, Yeni Nesil Teknoloji

WD'nin yeni nesil NASware 3.0 teknolojisi, NAS sistemlerindeki yaygın sabit sürücü sorunlarını azaltarak NAS depolama performansını arttırır. Yaygın sonuçlar, masaüstü bilgisayarlar için tasarlanan bir sabit sürücünün neden olduğu için uyumluluk, entegrasyon, yükseltilebilirlik, güvenilirlik ve mülkiyet maliyeti ile ilgilidir.

Daha Uzun Garanti Kapsamı

WD Red sabit sürücüleri, içiniz rahat ve daha uzun bir süre kullanabilmeniz için 3 yıl sınırlı garanti ve NAS sistemi üreticilerinin çoğuna uyan daha uzun bir garanti kapsamı ile desteklenir.
Daha Düşük İşletim Sıcaklıkları

WD Red sürücüler sayesinde elektrik faturanızı düşürün. Yenilikçi teknoloji, güç tüketimini azaltıp kullanım sıcaklığını düşürerek 7x24 açık kalan NAS ortamları için daha güvenilir ve uygun fiyatlı bir çözüm sunar.




Yardıma mı İhtiyacınız Var? Premium Destek sunuyoruz.

Tüm WD Red sabit sürücüleri, dünya çapında geçerli, 7/24 aktif (yalnızca İngilizce için geçerli, diğer diller için saatler değişmektedir) premium destek hattı da dahil profesyonel destek hizmetleri ve 3 yıllık sınırlı garanti ile birlikte temin edilir.
Aşağıdakiler için idealdir:

Küçük ofis ve ev ofisteki 1-8 arası sürücü yuvasına sahip NAS sistemleri ve RAID donanımlı PC'ler için özel olarak tasarlanmış ve test edilmiştir.

8 yuvadan fazlasını kullanan sistemler için lütfen WD Red Pro sabit sürücülerini deneyin.*

title: "Dell UltraSharp U2414H 23.8" Full HD IPS Monitor" 23.8 inch LED Monitor - 8ms | CCL Computers"
description:
"

                                See your work in vivid Full HD detail with a 23.8 inch monitor that features the world's thinnest border for nearly seamless viewing across multiple screens. With this incredible clarity across an ultra-wide 178-degree viewing angle comes the ability to pivot left-and right up to 90 degrees, so you can create a multiple screen arrangement with near-continual imagery between two or more monitors. In addition to 90-degree clockwise or counter-clockwise pivoting capability for use in side-by-side or top-to-top applications, the Dell UltraSharp 24 Monitor - U2414H offers generous height, tilt and swivel adjustments. Find the perfect position with 6.5-degree forward or 22-degree backward tilt adjustments and a height adjustability range of 130mm. An ultra-wide 178-degree viewing angle enables clear and easy sharing of your screen with multiple onlookers. Brilliance goes beyond the screen with easy connectivity to your favorite digital devices and fast USB charging capability. A mobile high-definition link (MHL) port allows you to view high-definition content directly from your compatible smart phone or tablet. Three USB 3.0 ports enable fast data transfers while one high-current USB 3.0 port supplies twice the power for charging and powering compatible USB devices. You can also connect your Dell UltraSharp 24 Monitor - U2414H to peripherals that require HDMI, DisplayPort or mini-DisplayPort connectivity.Manage power consumption wisely with PowerNap, enabled through the Dell Display Manager to either dim the monitor to the minimum brightness level or put it into sleep mode when it is not in use.

                            "

title: "UNIVERSAL AUDIO APOLLO 16 QUAD"@pt-pt QUAD - Woodbrass Portugal"@pt-pt
description: "Buy and register any new Apollo rackmount interface (Apollo 8, Apollo 8p, Apollo 16, or Apollo FireWire) through December 31st, 2017, and you’ll get a UAD-2 Satellite OCTO or QUAD DSP Accelerator absolutely free!For more information, please visit: https://www.uaudio.com/apollo-satellite-promoApollo 16 Thunderbolt Audio Interface w/ QUAD ProcessingThe new Apollo 16 is an elegant update to UA’s premium audio interface — delivering enhanced sound with the tone, feel, and flow of analog recording. Perfect for professional studios, this 18 x 20 Thunderbolt interface offers twice the analog connectivity of the Apollo 8/8p, making it ideal for pairing with mixing consoles and outboard processors. Apollo 16 further distinguishes itself with Realtime UAD Processing, letting you record at near-zero latency through the full range of UAD plug-ins from Neve, Studer, Manley, Lexicon, and more.* Apollo Expanded software now allows cascading up to four Apollos and six total UAD-2 devices in a single system over Thunderbolt (Mac), so you can scale up your studio as your needs grow. With its powerful onboard UAD-2 QUAD processing, genuine UA analog design, and next-generation A/D and D/A conversion, Apollo 16 puts class-leading audio performance in a sleek new package.Key Features● Next-generation Apollo A/D and D/A conversion for professional music production● Onboard UAD-2 QUAD Core DSP allows Realtime UAD Processing — record through plug-ins from Neve, Lexicon, Studer, Manley, Ampex, and more*● 18 x 20 Thunderbolt 2 audio interface for Mac with powerful Console 2.0 software control● 16 x 16 analog I/O via DB-25 connectors — ideal for pairing with mixing consoles, outboard preamps, etc.● Cascade up to 4 Apollo interfaces and 6 UAD devices total over Thunderbolt● Includes “Realtime Analog Classics Plus” UAD plug-in bundle with 610-B Tube Preamp & EQ, Raw Distortion, Softube Amp Rooms, legacy LA-2A, 1176, and Fairchild compressors, Pultec EQs, and more● World class UA analog design, superior components, and premium build qualityNext-Generation Apollo A/D and D/A ConversionApollo 16 improves upon the original Apollo’s gold-standard audio quality with completely redesigned, class-leading digital conversion — giving you increased dynamic range and even lower THD. This results in breathtaking clarity, depth, and accuracy in your recordings, from tracking and overdubbing, to mixing and mastering.Realtime UAD Plug-In Processing for Tracking, Mixing, and MasteringWhile Apollo 16’s “natural” sound is very open and transparent, it can quickly deliver a stunning range of classic analog tones and color via its Realtime UAD Processing. Available with generous UAD-2 QUAD processing onboard, Apollo’s DSP Acceleration allows for recording through UAD Powered Plug-Ins — with as low as sub-2ms latency — letting you monitor and “print” audio using classic analog emulations from Ampex, Lexicon, Manley, Neve, Roland, SSL, Studer, and more.* The Apollo 16’s bundled “Realtime Analog Classics Plus” suite of UAD plug-ins gives you the UA 610-B Tube Preamp & EQ, Raw Distortion, Softube Amp Rooms, legacy LA-2A, 1176, and Fairchild compressors, Pultec EQs, and more, so you have a rack full of bonafide audio classics, right out of the box.Using Apollo, UAD plug-ins are also available during mixing and mastering, putting UAD plug-ins (VST, RTAS, AU, AAX 64) at your disposal throughout the creative process. Apollo Expanded and Console 2.0Thanks to Apollo Expanded software, users of Thunderbolt-equipped Apollo Twin, Apollo 8, Apollo 8p, and Apollo 16 audio interfaces can combine up to four Apollos and six total UAD-2 devices — adding I/O and DSP as their studio grows. Apollo Expanded also provides seamless integration with previous generation Apollos over Thunderbolt. With Apollo 16’s Console 2.0 application — a complete re-imagining of Apollo’s original Console software — you can take advantage of over 25 user-requested features such as Channel Strip presets, Drag & Drop functionality, dynamically resizable windows, and more.*All trademarks are recognized as property of their respective owners. title: "TP-Link TL-WN881ND 300Mbps Wireless N PCI Express Adaptor" "Server Case UK - TP-Link
description:
"Wireless N PCI Express 2.0(x1) Adaptor TL-WN881ND allows you to connect a desktop computer to a wireless network and access high-speed Internet connection. Comply with IEEE 802.11n, they provide wireless speed up to 300Mbps, which is beneficial for the online gaming or even HD video streaming. MIMO (multiple input, multiple output antennas) technology, it shows more excellent abilities of mitigating data loss over long distances and through obstacles in a small office or a large apartment, even in a steel-and-concrete building. Above all, you could easily pick up the wireless network during long-distance connection where legacy 11g products may not! Clear Channel Assessment (CCA) automatically avoids channel conflicts using its clear channel selection feature and fully realizes the advantages of channel binding, greatly enhanced the wireless performance. As for the security of WI-FI connection, WEP encryption has been no longer the strongest and safest guards for outside intrusions. TL-WN881ND provides WPA/WPA2 encryptions that are created by the WI-FI Alliance industry group, promoting interpretabilities and security for WLAN, which could effectively and efficiently protect the wireless network.TL-WN881ND comes with a CD with utility that helps you complete the software installation and wireless network settings, including security configurations and wireless connection, which is convenient for users, even for novice users.Features

Wireless N speed up to 300Mbps makes it ideal for video streaming, online gaming and Internet calls
2T2R MIMO delivers greater throughput at range versus conventional 1T1R
Easily setup a highly secured wireless link with QSS software embedded
Supports 64/128 WEP, WPA /WPA2/WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK(TKIP/AES), supports IEEE 802.1X
Supports Windows 7 32/64bit, Windows XP 32/64bit, Vista 32/64bit
Supports ad-hoc and infrastructure mode
Bundled utility provides quick & hassle free installation
Seamlessly compatible with 802.11n/b/g products
Wireless Modes: Ad-Hoc / Infrastructure mode

title: "Crucial - DDR4 4 GB DIMM 288-pin" " Crucial 288-pin CT4G4RFS8213 Server Memory CDW.com
description: "More speed. More bandwidth. More efficient. Next generation DDR4 memory is here.Overcome one of your greatest server limitations: memory. From networking, cloud computing, and virtualization to HPC, Big Data and more, memory - dependent server applications require increasingly higher densities of memory and higher levels of performance than are attainable on current DDR3 technology. Enter Crucial DDR4 server memory.This product is a 4GB DDR4 server module that operates at speeds up to 2133 MT/s and has a CL15 latency. It is a Registerred DIMM (RDIMM) with Error Correction Code (ECC). It conforms to the industry standard DDR4 RDIMM layout of 288 pins and is compatible with systems that take DDR4 2133MT/s RDIMM memory."

title: "HPE Smart Array P421/2GB with FBWC - storage controller (RAID) SATA 6Gb/s" " HPE 6Gb/s 631674-B21 RAID Controllers CDWG.com
description: "The HPE Smart Array P421 Controller is a low profile, 6 Gb/s, PCIe 3.0, Serial Attached SCSI (SAS) RAID controller that provides enterprise class, storage performance, maximum external scalability, and data protection for select HP ProLiant Gen8 rack and tower servers. It features eight external SAS ports and delivers increased server uptime by providing advanced storage functionality, including online RAID level migration (between any RAID levels) with flash back write cache, global online spare, and pre-failure warning. Data Compatibility among all models of Smart Array controllers allows simple and easy migration at any time when needs for higher performance, capacity, and availability increase. Even new generations of Smart Array controllers can understand the data format of previous generations of Smart Array controllers."

Speck's SmartShell® GLITTER case fits the 13-inch MacBook Pro with Touch Bar and 13-inch MacBook Pro without Touch Bar (2016 models).

Speck's SmartShell GLITTER MacBook Pro 13" case combines sparkling glitter crystals with a sleek hardshell design for shimmering protection against scratches, dents, and bumps.

This SmartShell GLITTER MacBook Pro 13" case is designed for superior protection and durability. It's 47% stronger against bumps and punctures than our previous SeeThru cases. Redesigned corner clips hold the case securely onto your 13-inch MacBook Pro with Touch Bar and are 60% stronger than the clips on SeeThru cases to prevent breakage.

Glitter crystals in the SmartShell GLITTER MacBook Pro 13" with Touch Bar cases add sparkle and shine to your MacBook. Our non-metallic glitter crystals are embedded in the case, so they won't scratch off or interfere with your computer’s connectivity. Our non-metallic glitter won't interfere with your computer's connectivity.

This lightweight, slim glitter MacBook Pro 13" case is easy to install and fits closely to protect your MacBook against scratches. Rubberized feet on the bottom of the case keep your MacBook from sliding around on smooth surfaces.


"@en

title: "Transcend JetFlash 500 - USB flash drive 8 GB" " Transcend GB TS8GJF500 Thumb Drives CDW.com
description: "Losing USB end caps can be quite annoying, not to mention the inconvenience of taking the cap on and off every time the drive is used. For extra convenience and protection, the JetFlash 500 flash drive is designed with an extension and retraction mechanism that enables users to bring out or hide the connector with a single flick of the thumb. Its capless design not only keeps dust and debris out of the drive, but also ensures there is no cap to misplace or lose.Thanks to its use of ultrasonic welding technology, the JetFlash 500 drive's inseparable outer case not only makes the drive more solid and rugged, but also improves its tactile and visual appeal. The JetFlash 500 is a USB flash drive you will want to take out of your pocket and show off to your friends."

description: "The OCZ RD400A NVM Express M.2 solid state drive series are designed to propel high-end computing into a new realm of possibility. The OCZ RD400A PCIe Gen3 x4 outperforms SATA SSDs by over 4.5 times in sequential read, and over 3 times in sequential write performance so your system won't be deprived of the storage bandwidth your data-intensive workload requires. The OCZ RD400's next generation NVMe interface provides a more responsive PC experience with shorter storage latency than that of today's traditional hard disk drives and SATA SSDs. Along with high performance, the OCZ RD400 is designed for mobile, desktop, or workstation applications."

title: "Logitech Performance MX"@en
description:
"
                        Logitech Performance Mouse MXThe power to achieve more on more surfacesYour hand is poised. You're set to create the big presentation. And with your Logitech Performance Mouse MX, nothing stands in your way. This is the mouse that puts high performance in the palm of your hand.







Precision cursor control on more surfaces, including glass where other mice fail
Wireless freedom for multiple devices with plug-and-forget Unifying receiver
Flexible recharging through your computer or a wall outlet
Fingertip controls for hyper-fast scrolling, quick-zoom and more
Sculpted design cradles your hand for unmatched comfort 





New Darkfield Tracking—now you can work on surfaces like glass, granite and polished wood without a restrictive mouse pad. Flexible USB or AC recharging eliminates the need to buy or change batteries. 
Darkfield Laser Tracking for precise cursor control—even on glassThe culmination of a groundbreaking five-year engineering effort, Darkfield Laser Tracking lets you track on more surfaces than ever—including glass, where other mice flat-out fail. Logitech's exclusive technology tracks mouse movements by producing a detailed micro-roadmap of the work surface. So now you can confidently use your mouse on surfaces you never could before like clear glass, lacquered wood and marble.
Plug-and-forget Logitech Unifying receiver stays in your computerOne tiny wireless receiver gives you many possibilities. The receiver is so small you can leave it in your notebook and forget about it. So you never need to unplug it when you move around, and your mouse is always ready when you are. Plus, this one receiver connects up to 6 Unifying compatible devices, allowing you to add accessories like a Unifying wireless keyboard without having to manage multiple USB receivers. Create The Combo That Works For You.
Flexible recharging system ends battery hassles and downtimeRecharge your mouse anytime, anywhere—even while you work. Use the USB cable for charging through your computer. Or use the AC power supply to plug the mouse into your wall outlet. Either way, your mouse is always charged and ready when you are. From now on, you'll never need to look for batteries to get your mouse back in action so you can get back to work.
Fly through long documents at a spin of the Hyper-fast scroll wheel. 
Hyper-fast scroll wheel puts you in total scroll control 20-page spreadsheet? Extra-long email thread? Spin the almost frictionless scroll wheel to fly through long documents, emails and web pages. Tilt the wheel left and right for side-to-side scrolling. You can even shift to click-by-click mode for precise, line-by-line navigation of lists, slides and photos. Fast or slow, you've got the control to get it done at your pace.
Convenient thumb buttons help you to quickly flip through web histories.
Sculpted shape guides your hand for more control and comfortImagine a mouse that feels so natural in your hand you actually forget you're using a mouse. The sculpted design cradles your hand for more comfort and less fatigue, even during marathon mouse sessions. And every control is intelligently positioned right at your fingertips, so you're in total control of every click, scroll, cut, paste and zoom.
 
 
 
 
 
 
                    "@en
